tags: [ development, drawing ]
---


DRAWING CONTROLS
            | Click | Red line
 Shift      | Click | Green line
 Ctrl       | Click | Blue line
 Alt        | Click | Red highlighter
 Alt+Shift  | Click | Green highlighter
 Alt+Ctrl   | Click | Blue highlighter
            | F10   | Undo
Shift       | F10   | Redo


PROGRAM CONTROLS
Ctrl   | F9    | Toggle visibility ON/OFF
       | F9    | Toggle drawing ON/OFF
Shift  | F9    | Delete lines
Alt    | F9    | Quit program
